snippet.title: We Are The Caretakers Announcement Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing We Are The Caretakers, an original sci-fi squad management RPG from Heart Shaped Games (creators of Hero Generations). Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1042960/We_Are_The_Caretakers/

Join The Movement On Discord. Get updates and bonus content from the developers - https://discord.gg/wearethecaretakers

Learn more at http://www.wearethecaretakers.com.
